{"title":"Docker常用命令","date":"2020-05-14T04:26:49.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"May 14, 2020","L":"05/14/2020","MM-DD":"05-14"},"link":"2020/05/14/docker-command","tags":["Docker"],"categories":["Docker"],"updated":"2021-03-11T18:49:34.599Z","content":"<h2 id=\"安装/运行\">安装/运行<a title=\"#安装/运行\" href=\"#安装/运行\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"查找镜像\">查找镜像<a title=\"#查找镜像\" href=\"#查找镜像\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker search &lt;image_name&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><code>image_name</code> 镜像名称</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 查找helloword镜像</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">docker search helloworld</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"拉取镜像到本地\">拉取镜像到本地<a title=\"#拉取镜像到本地\" href=\"#拉取镜像到本地\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker pull &lt;image_name&gt;&lt;:tag&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><code>image_name</code> 镜像名称。</li>\n<li><code>:tag</code> 镜像标签，表示拉取指定tag的镜像，比如<code>image_name:1.0</code>，默认为<code>latest</code></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 拉取最新的helloworld镜像</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">docker pull helloworld:latest</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"运行容器\">运行容器<a title=\"#运行容器\" href=\"#运行容器\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker run -itd -rm --name &lt;container_name&gt; -p 80:80 &lt;image_name&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><code>--name container_name</code> 容器命名为<code>&lt;container_name&gt;</code></li>\n<li><code>-rm</code> 容器在退出时自动删除</li>\n<li><code>-d</code> 后台运行容器，并返回容器ID</li>\n<li><code>_e</code> 设置容器参数（环境变量）</li>\n<li><code>-p 80:80</code> 将本地计算机上的端口<code>80</code>映射到容器中的端口<code>80</code></li>\n<li><code>-v xx:xxx</code> 将本地路径绑定到容器中的路径</li>\n<li><code>image_name</code> 镜像名称</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"示例一\">示例一<a title=\"#示例一\" href=\"#示例一\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 运行helloworld镜像，这里没有指定--name，系统将随机命名容器</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">docker run helloworld</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"示例二\">示例二<a title=\"#示例二\" href=\"#示例二\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># --name alsync.web 容器命名为alsync.web</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># -rm 容器在退出时自动删除</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># -d 后台运行</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># -p 5000:80 将本地计算机上的端口 5000 映射到容器中的端口 80</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">docker run -it --rm -p 5000:80 --name alsync.web alsync.web</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"显示容器/镜像\">显示容器/镜像<a title=\"#显示容器/镜像\" href=\"#显示容器/镜像\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"显示容器\">显示容器<a title=\"#显示容器\" href=\"#显示容器\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker ps &lt;-a|-q|-aq&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><code>-a</code> 显示所有的容器，包括未运行的</li>\n<li><code>-q</code> 静默模式，只显示容器编号</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 显示所有的容器，默认为运行中的</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">docker ps</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 显示所有的容器，包括未运行的</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">docker ps -a</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 显示所有容器的编号</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">docker ps -aq</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"显示镜像\">显示镜像<a title=\"#显示镜像\" href=\"#显示镜像\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker images</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"启动/停止容器\">启动/停止容器<a title=\"#启动/停止容器\" href=\"#启动/停止容器\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker start/stop &lt;container&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><code>container</code> 容器名称或者容器ID</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"批量启动所有容器\">批量启动所有容器<a title=\"#批量启动所有容器\" href=\"#批量启动所有容器\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker start $(docker ps -a | awk <span class=\"string\">'&#123; print $1&#125;'</span> | tail -n +2)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"批量停止所有容器\">批量停止所有容器<a title=\"#批量停止所有容器\" href=\"#批量停止所有容器\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker stop $(docker ps -a | awk <span class=\"string\">'&#123; print $1&#125;'</span> | tail -n +2)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"删除容器/镜像\">删除容器/镜像<a title=\"#删除容器/镜像\" href=\"#删除容器/镜像\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"删除容器\">删除容器<a title=\"#删除容器\" href=\"#删除容器\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker rm &lt;container&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><code>container</code> 容器名称或者容器ID</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"删除所有的容器\">删除所有的容器<a title=\"#删除所有的容器\" href=\"#删除所有的容器\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker rm $(docker ps -a -q)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 或者</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">docker rm $(docker ps -aq)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"删除镜像\">删除镜像<a title=\"#删除镜像\" href=\"#删除镜像\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker rmi &lt;image&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><code>image</code> 镜像ID或者名称</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"删除所有untagged镜像\">删除所有untagged镜像<a title=\"#删除所有untagged镜像\" href=\"#删除所有untagged镜像\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker rmi $(docker images | grep <span class=\"string\">\"^&lt;none&gt;\"</span> | awk <span class=\"string\">\"&#123;print <span class=\"variable\">$3</span>&#125;\"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"删除所有镜像\">删除所有镜像<a title=\"#删除所有镜像\" href=\"#删除所有镜像\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker rmi $(docker images -q)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"进入容器\">进入容器<a title=\"#进入容器\" href=\"#进入容器\"></a></h2>\n<p>部分容器有bash命令，我们还可以通过执行bash进入到容器中查看文件信息</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker <span class=\"built_in\">exec</span> -it &lt;container_name&gt; /bin/bash</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><code>container_name</code> 容器名称</li>\n</ul>\n<p>启动某个服务/代理</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sh &lt;agent/services.sh&gt; start</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><code>agent/services.sh</code> 服务/代理文件名</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"重启docker服务\">重启docker服务<a title=\"#重启docker服务\" href=\"#重启docker服务\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo systemctl restart docker.service <span class=\"comment\"># 重启docker服务</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em>重启后所有的docker容器都退出了，需要重新启动</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"daemon.json\">daemon.json<a title=\"#daemon.json\" href=\"#daemon.json\"></a></h2>\n<p>docker配置文件，如果刚安装完docker该文件应该是不存在的，需要手动<code>vi(m) daemon.json</code>创建，位于<code>/etc/docker</code>目录下面</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\"># docker镜像源，官方镜像地址如果不能下载可更换</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">\"registry-mirrors\"</span>: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"http://hub-mirror.c.163.com\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"http://f1361db2.m.daocloud.io\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    ],</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">\"insecure-registries\"</span>:[<span class=\"string\">\"192.168.222.135:5000\"</span>],</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">\"log-driver\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"json-file\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">\"log-opts\"</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\"># 日志最大文件为10m</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"max-size\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"10m\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"max-file\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"5\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"远程管理\">远程管理<a title=\"#远程管理\" href=\"#远程管理\"></a></h2>\n<p>docker支持远程管理，比如portainer连接，需要开启2375端口</p>\n<h3 id=\"修改docker.service\">修改docker.service<a title=\"#修改docker.service\" href=\"#修改docker.service\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">vim /lib/systemd/system/docker.service</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 找到ExecStart参数并替换为下面代码</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">ExecStart=/usr/bin/dockerd -H unix:///var/run/docker.sock -H tcp://0.0.0.0:2375</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em>实际有三种方法可以修改，具体实现方式可自行Google</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"重启\">重启<a title=\"#重启\" href=\"#重启\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">systemctl daemon-reload</span><br><span class=\"line\">systemctl restart docker</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"相关链接\">相关链接<a title=\"#相关链接\" href=\"#相关链接\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.runoob.com/docker/docker-command-manual.html\" title=\"Docker命令大全\" target=\"_blank\">Docker命令大全</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_32447301/article/details/79387649\" title=\"Docker删除容器与镜像\" target=\"_blank\">Docker删除容器与镜像</a></li>\n</ul>\n","prev":{"title":"自定义Code First约定","link":"2020/06/03/custom-code-first-conventions"},"next":{"title":"Docker安装teamcity","link":"2020/05/13/docker-install-teamcity"},"plink":"http://blog.arytry.com/2020/05/14/docker-command/","toc":[{"id":"安装/运行","title":"安装&#x2F;运行","index":"1","children":[{"id":"查找镜像","title":"查找镜像","index":"1.1"},{"id":"拉取镜像到本地","title":"拉取镜像到本地","index":"1.2"},{"id":"运行容器","title":"运行容器","index":"1.3"}]},{"id":"显示容器/镜像","title":"显示容器&#x2F;镜像","index":"2","children":[{"id":"显示容器","title":"显示容器","index":"2.1"},{"id":"显示镜像","title":"显示镜像","index":"2.2"}]},{"id":"启动/停止容器","title":"启动&#x2F;停止容器","index":"3","children":[{"id":"批量启动所有容器","title":"批量启动所有容器","index":"3.1"},{"id":"批量停止所有容器","title":"批量停止所有容器","index":"3.2"}]},{"id":"删除容器/镜像","title":"删除容器&#x2F;镜像","index":"4","children":[{"id":"删除容器","title":"删除容器","index":"4.1"},{"id":"删除所有的容器","title":"删除所有的容器","index":"4.2"},{"id":"删除镜像","title":"删除镜像","index":"4.3"},{"id":"删除所有untagged镜像","title":"删除所有untagged镜像","index":"4.4"},{"id":"删除所有镜像","title":"删除所有镜像","index":"4.5"}]},{"id":"进入容器","title":"进入容器","index":"5"},{"id":"重启docker服务","title":"重启docker服务","index":"6"},{"id":"daemon.json","title":"daemon.json","index":"7"},{"id":"远程管理","title":"远程管理","index":"8","children":[{"id":"修改docker.service","title":"修改docker.service","index":"8.1"},{"id":"重启","title":"重启","index":"8.2"}]},{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","index":"9"}],"reward":true}